George W. Thomas, Plaintiff in Error, v. The State of Florida, Defendant in Error. (Supreme Court of Florida, En Banc, June Term, 1909.) Attorney General, for Defendant in Error. Criminal Court of Eecord of Walton County; D. Stuart Gillis, Judge.

No appearance for Plaintiff in Error.

Judgment against plaintiff in error. Writ of error dismissed on motion of the Attorney General.
